Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
sizeof_collection(25.10)                              sizeof_collection(25.10)

Name
       sizeof_collection  -  Returns  the total number of objects contained in
       the specified collection

Syntax
        sizeof_collection

       [-help]

       <collection>

       Returns the total number of objects contained in the specified  collec-
       tion.   If   the   collection  contains  different  types  of  objects,
       sizeof_collection returns the sum of all the objects of different types
       in the collection.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <collection>
              Specifies the collection.

Related Information
              * add_to_collection

              * append_to_collection

              * compare_collections

              * copy_collection

              * filter_collection

